From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OpenWrt Build System <openwrt@localhost>
Date: Sat, 27 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ath11k: fix uninitialized tx status flags

ath11k_dp_tx_complete_msdu() checks ATH11K_SKB_TX_STATUS while deciding
whether it can drop completion processing when stats_disable is set, but
the local flags variable is never initialized in that path.

Use the skb control block flags, matching the HTT completion path.

--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/dp_tx.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/dp_tx.c
@@ -720,6 +720,7 @@ static void ath11k_dp_tx_complete_msdu(s
 	rel_status = FIELD_GET(HAL_WBM_RELEASE_INFO0_TQM_RELEASE_REASON,
 			       tx_status->info0);
 
+	flags = skb_cb->flags;
  	/* Free skb here if stats is disabled */
 	if (ab->stats_disable && !(flags & ATH11K_SKB_TX_STATUS)) {
 		if (msdu->destructor) {
